  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AuditLoggingComponent, VirtualConnectorExtension, IntegrationConnector, LineageIntegratorOMISConnector, OpenMetadataTopicListener
    public class OpenLineageEventReceiverIntegrationConnector
extends LineageIntegratorConnector
implements OpenMetadataTopicListener
    OpenLineageEventReceiverIntegrationConnector receives open lineage events from an event broker such as an Apache Kafka topic. It publishes them to other listening lineage integration connectors.
